Detailed Description

The IpoptSolver class solves problems using Ipopt.

Author:
Robert Fourer, Jun Ma, Kipp Martin
Version:
1.0, 03/14/2004
Since:
OS 1.0
Remarks:
this class takes an OSiL instance and optimizes it using the COIN-OR Ipopt solver
